
README file
-----------

This package contains several utility files for stream analysis,
string conversion, primitive time handling, etc. In the subdirectory
doc/ you can find a postscript documentation.

Read INSTALL if you want to know how to compile this package. The
package has been developed under Linux, using the egcs-2.91.66 C++
compiler. The package has been successfully used on the following
platforms/compilers:

  Linux 2.2.3 (PC) / egcs-2.91.66
  Digital unix v4.0B (rev 564) / Compaq C++ V6.2-024
  Windows NT / Microsoft Visual Studio Prof. 5.1
  IRIX 6.2 / CC

See AUTHORS file for contact information.

